-- Petrobras CEO Says Fuel Price Will Have to Go Up, Globo Reports
-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 2012-02-15T11:39:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-15/petrobras-ceo-says-fuel-price-will-have-to-go-up-globo-reports.html
Brazilian fuel prices will have to
increase at some point, newspaper O Globo cited Petroleo
Brasileiro SA’s new chief executive officer, Maria das Gracas
Foster, as saying.  Petrobras, as the Rio de Janeiro-based oil producer is
known, had a bad third quarter performance which can’t become a
trend, Foster told Globo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
